*** These laces are for your Sunbed - Siesta, Siesta L,&nbsp;LP3 etc&nbsp;***If you are unsure if these are the laces you need just check,&nbsp;If you have no arm rests and can lie completely horizontal then these are the&nbsp;laces you need.&nbsp; If your chair has arm rests then&nbsp;laces for the RSXSometimes heavy wear and tear can cause the cord laces on your sunbed&nbsp;to wear away and become frayed. On the swing tags of laced chairs Lafuma recommend that 'the elastic laces should be replaced when they show signs of wear (especially in the front of the seat) and at least every two years.' 

For a fraction of the price of a new sunbed, Lafuma’s replacement lacing cords allows you to replace the cords easily at home; refurbishing your sunbed&nbsp;instantly. One pack of lacing cords will be enough to completely re-lace your sunbed.&nbsp; You will recieve a single lace of 8 metres, which you then cut to suit your particular sunbed.&nbsp;

Please note that Lafuma consider the lacing cords to be a consumable part, as they will wear differently dependent on use, therefore these are not covered by the Lafuma guarantee.
